      "message": "\u003e I don\u0027t think we need to worry about /prefetch for this use. We could also maybe sneak it in with --monitor-self\u003d\"--type\u003dcrashpad-handler /prefetch:7\"?\n\nThe command line is built by a series of calls to https://crashpad.chromium.org/doxygen/namespacecrashpad.html#a52a7dee343e392e5bf1794e8136df7f9, so that’d just wind up as a single argument on the other side, and Chrome wouldn’t recognize process type “crashpad-handler /prefetch:7”.",
